<li>Yaakov Kraftmakher, "<i><a href="http://www.iop.org/EJ/abstract/0143-0807/22/5/302" class="external text" title="http://www.iop.org/EJ/abstract/0143-0807/22/5/302" rel="nofollow">Two experiments with rotating magnetic field</a></i>". 2001 Eur. J. Phys. 22 477-482.</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>Bogdan Mielnik and David J. Fernández C., "<i><a href="http://scitation.aip.org/getabs/servlet/GetabsServlet?prog=normal&amp;id=JMAPAQ000030000002000537000001&amp;idtype=cvips&amp;gifs=yes" class="external text" title="http://scitation.aip.org/getabs/servlet/GetabsServlet?prog=normal&amp;id=JMAPAQ000030000002000537000001&amp;idtype=cvips&amp;gifs=yes" rel="nofollow">An electron trapped in a rotating magnetic field</a></i>". Journal of Mathematical Physics, February 1989, Volume 30, Issue 2, pp. 537-549.</li>
</ul>
<ul>
<li>Sonia Melle, Miguel A. Rubio and Gerald G. Fuller "<i><a href="http://prola.aps.org/abstract/PRE/v61/i4/p4111_1" class="external text" title="http://prola.aps.org/abstract/PRE/v61/i4/p4111_1" rel="nofollow">Structure and dynamics of magnetorheological fluids in rotating magnetic fields</a></i>". Phys. Rev. E 61, 4111 – 4117 (2000).</li>
</ul>


